AmiNet-calc V1.1 (23.3.94)

What:

Calculates size of an AmiNet-On-Disc-order.

Kind:

Public-Domain. You can do everything with it! BUT: THIS IS NOT
TRUE FOR included reqtools and rexxreqtools-libraries! ...

